text = "WASD - Pan | Scroll - Zoom
R - Regen | T - Wire | F - Fog

ENGINEERING (1-9):
1-Clear 2-Flatten 3-Trench
4-Road 5-Berm 6-Foxhole
7-Crater 8-DetLine 9-DetSq
0 - Damage | ESC - Cancel
M - Place LZ Markers

Left Click - Execute"

